---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — Bravura Builders"
  description="NYC discipline brought home to Atlanta. Founder Joseph Kievman and the Bravura standard for every remodel, bath, and build-out."
>
  <section class="page-hero dark on-dark">
    <div class="wrap">
      <span class="eyebrow">About Bravura</span>
      <h1>NYC discipline, brought home to Atlanta.</h1>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section>
    <div class="wrap story">
      <div>
        <p class="big rv">
          Before Bravura, founder Joseph Kievman spent four years running large-scale gut
          renovations of multi-story Manhattan buildings in the most demanding construction market
          in the world.
        </p>
        <div class="body rv">
          <p>
            As a senior project manager at MGC, a New York City construction firm, he ran full
            residential remodels and multi-story gut renovations where a slipped schedule cost real
            money and there was no room for &ldquo;we&rsquo;ll figure it out later.&rdquo;
          </p>
          <p>
            <b>Bravura Builders brings that intensity to the Atlanta metro:</b> scheduling discipline,
            transparent line-item pricing, deposit and milestone payment terms in writing, and subcontractors
            held to the same scope you signed.
          </p>
          <p>
            The name is the standard. <i>Bravura</i>: great technical skill and brilliance shown in
            a performance. That&rsquo;s the bar for every kitchen, every bath, every build-out that
            carries the logo.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <aside class="founder rv">
        <span class="role">Founder &amp; CEO</span>
        <h3>Joseph Kievman</h3>
        <p>
          General contractor and former senior PM on Manhattan gut renovations. Still walks every
          Bravura site.
        </p>
        <ul class="creds">
          <li>4 years senior project management, MGC, New York City</li>
          <li>Multi-story residential gut renovations</li>
          <li>Licensed &amp; insured, Georgia</li>
          <li>Based in Alpharetta &middot; serving Atlanta metro</li>
        </ul>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="cta-band" style="padding-top:0">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="cta-box rv">
        <div>
          <h2>Work with us.</h2>
          <p>Construction estimates are free. Design starts with a conversation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="actions">
          <a class="btn blue" href="/contact">Get in touch <span class="arr">&rarr;</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
